      "speaker": "Elena",
      "text": "¡Qué calor hace hoy!",
      "translation": "It's so hot today!",
      "ipa": "[ke kaˈloɾ ˈase ˈoj]",
      "dialect": "es-MX",
      "audio_asset_id": "a1-wx-mx-001",
      "alternate_phrasing": [],
      "context": "Commenting on hot weather"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Diego",
      "text": "Sí, hace mucho calor. ¿Cuál es el pronóstico para mañana?",
      "translation": "Yes, it's very hot. What's the forecast for tomorrow?",
      "ipa": "[ˈsi ˈase ˈmutʃo kaˈloɾ ‖ ˈkwal es el pɾoˈnostiko ˈpaɾa maˈɲana]",
      "dialect": "es-MX",
      "audio_asset_id": "a1-wx-mx-002",
      "alternate_phrasing": [],
      "context": "Asking about weather forecast"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Elena",
      "text": "Dicen que va a llover por la tarde.",
      "translation": "They say it's going to rain in the afternoon.",
      "ipa": "[ˈðiθen ke βa a ʝoˈβeɾ poɾ la ˈtaɾðe]",
      "dialect": "es-MX",
      "audio_asset_id": "a1-wx-mx-003",
      "alternate_phrasing": [],
      "context": "Sharing weather forecast"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Diego",
      "text": "¡Ay! Entonces necesito llevar paraguas.",
