      "dialect": "es-MX",
      "audio_asset_id": "a1-wx-mx-005",
      "alternate_phrasing": [],
      "context": "Asking about hometown weather"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Diego",
      "text": "En Monterrey hace mucho calor en verano. En invierno es fresco.",
      "translation": "In Monterrey it's very hot in summer. In winter it's cool.",
      "ipa": "[en monteˈrej ˈase ˈmutʃo kaˈloɾ en βeˈɾano ‖ en imˈbjeɾno es ˈfɾesko]",
      "dialect": "es-MX",
      "audio_asset_id": "a1-wx-mx-006",
      "alternate_phrasing": [],
      "context": "Describing seasonal weather in hometown"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "Elena",
      "text": "Aquí en la Ciudad de México llueve mucho en verano.",
